<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pet a Dog | User Profile</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body style="background-color: rgb(244, 245, 246);">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg fixed-top navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/home">
                <img src="../imgs/rover.png" alt="" style="width: 100px;">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarSupportedContent"
                aria-controls="navbarSupportedContent" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarSupportedContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mr-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/home">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/search-sitter">Search a Sitter</a>
                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/services">Our Services</a>
                    </li>

                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/dog-care">Dog Care</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="form-inline my-2 my-lg-0">
                    <a href="/profile">View Profile</a>
                    <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST">
                        <button id="log-out-btn" class="btn btn-primary ml-4" type="submit">Log out</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container" style="margin-top: 5rem;">
        <div class="card mb-3" style="max-width: 100%;">
            <div class="row no-gutters">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <img src="../imgs/profile.png" class="card-img" style="padding: 1rem;">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title"><%= userData.firstName %></h5>
                        <p class="card-text">Email: <%= userData.email %></p>
                        <p class="card-text"><a href="/profile/add">Add your Dog</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <% for (var i of dogData) { %>
        <div class="card mt-3">
            <div class="card-header">
                About your dog <%= i.name %>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                        <p class="card-text">Sex: <%= i.gender %></p>
                        <p class="card-text">Age: <%= i.ageYears %> years, <%= i.ageMonths %> months old </p>
                        <p class="card-text">Weight: <%= i.weight %> lbs </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <p class="card-text">Breed: <%= i.breed %></p>
                        <p class="card-text">Tracking Chip: <%= i.isMicrochipped %></p>
                        <p class="card-text">House Trained: <%= i.isTrained %></p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <p class="card-text">Gets along with children: <%= i.children %></p>
                        <p class="card-text">Gets along with other dogs: <%= i.nature %></p>
                        <p class="card-text">Gets along with cats: <%= i.cats %></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <footer class="container-fluid page-footer font-small bg-info pt-4 mt-4">
        <div class="container text-center text-md-left">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-md-0 mt-3">
                    <h5 class="text-uppercase font-weight-bold">Footer text 1</h5>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Expedita sapiente sint, nulla, nihil
                        repudiandae commodi voluptatibus corrupti animi sequi aliquid magnam debitis, maxime quam
                        recusandae
                        harum esse fugiat. Itaque, culpa?</p>

                </div>

                <hr class="clearfix w-100 d-md-none pb-3">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-md-0 mb-3">
                    <h5 class="text-uppercase font-weight-bold">Footer text 2</h5>
                    <p>Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Optio deserunt fuga perferendis modi
                        earum
                        commodi aperiam temporibus quod nulla nesciunt aliquid debitis ullam omnis quos ipsam,
                        aspernatur id
                        excepturi hic.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
        <div class="container-fluid footer-copyright text-center py-3 bg-info">
            Â© 2020 A Place for Rover, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
            711 Capitol Way S., Suite 204, Olympia, WA 98501
